📹 Live Session App

An interactive live video session platform built with Next.js, TypeScript, and MongoDB.
Users can create live sessions, share unique links, and manage sessions in real-time.

⚡ Tech Stack

Next.js 14 (App Router)

React 18 + TypeScript

Tailwind CSS + Shadcn/UI + Framer Motion

MongoDB (native driver)

pnpm as the package manager

🧩 Setup
1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/live-session-app.git
cd live-session-app

2. Install dependencies
pnpm install

3. Create a .env.local file
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@cluster0.ja1ydej.mongodb.net/

4. Run the development server
pnpm dev


The app will start at 👉 http://localhost:3000

✅ Test MongoDB Connection
node --env-file=.env.local test-db-connection.mjs


If successful:

✅ Connected to MongoDB
📦 Database: live_sessions

